strategies.name: Swing Trading (Multi-Timeframe)
strategies.description: Swing analysis using Daily/4H trend and liquidity zones.
strategies.details: Analyze charts with Daily/4H trend, liquidity sweeps, and 20/50 EMA pullbacks. Outputs actionable entry, SL, TP levels and R:R.

strategies.name: Scalping (Seconds → Minutes)
strategies.description: EMA-tap, BoS and sweep entries in 1m–5m with 1H filter.
strategies.details: Trade in higher timeframe trend using 20/50 EMA filter and fast triggers. Tight SL (5–10 pips) with 1:1 to 1:2 targets.

strategies.name: Day Trading (Intraday)
strategies.description: 4H→1H bias, session liquidity, FVG and EMA retests.
strategies.details: Trade intraday using session levels, sweeps and continuation setups. Minimum R:R = 1:2; manage through TP1/TP2 and move to BE.

parameters.Triggers: BoS, Sweep + Rejection, EMA Retest, FVG
